Step 2 : Using template inheritance

Step 3 : Add styling
/*static/css/style.css*/
footer a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #f39c12;
}

include this in your CSS
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{% static 'css/style.css' %}">

Step 4 : Replace with real links
<a href="https://facebook.com/placeholder">Facebook</a>


